skins.shipDescription: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine ®C U-556.
skins.selfIntroduction: I swore an oath to Neptune himself, that I would protect Lord Bismarck from danger, no matter where she encountered it! ... But there are still some things I can't handle by myself. Ahahaha...
skins.acquisition: Ahoy! Type VIIC submarine U-556 here! This is my home port, no question! Oh, right, is Lord Bismarck here?
skins.login: Welcome back! Don't you feel super pumped on a day like this?
skins.details: Grrryyeeaaaargh! Come at mee!! Haaaah... haaaah... sometimes I get stuck in war mode and need to calm myself down. Ahahahahaa!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Commander, if you don't play with me I'm just going to go find Lord Bismarck
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander, let's go swimming! Don't worry, I'll keep you safe!
skins.secretaryIdle3: Commander, sitting too long is bad for your health!
skins.secretaryTouch: Come on, Commander. Can we go play with Lord Bismarck?

skins.shipDescription: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!
skins.acquisition: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!
skins.login: I've heard parties are suuuuuuuuuuper fun! I can't wait!!
skins.details: Hey, Commander, can we go check out the kitchen? ... Oh, they're really busy in there? I guess we better not get in their way...
skins.secretaryIdle1: Don't give me that face, kitty. Here, look, it's my finger. It's over here! ... Now it's over here!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander, have you seen Lord Bismarck? Can we go look for her?
skins.secretaryIdle3: Om nom nom. Delicious! This is really good! Here, Commander, try some!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Hmph! Don't think you're gonna get away with that!
